{
  "stem": "26765.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the bodies were unloaded and then the Russian soldiers, they turned to us, the survivors and they said, well, you can go into that little town and just go into the houses.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we said, well, how was that possible?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they said, well, the houses are empty and they were.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And a family Stern, Mr. and Mrs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Stern, asked us to share a house with them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They had two daughters and the train had stopped outside a very small little town in a section of Germany called Saxony.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The name of the town is Trobitz.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "At that time, it had inhabitants of about 800 people, so small.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And indeed, there were no people in that town, at least I didn't see any people in that town.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And because the Germans were very afraid of the Russians and when they anticipated that they would take over their town or their city, they fled.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So we moved into this home with Mr. and Mrs.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Stern.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Then George and I, we took a little cart and we went from house to house looking for food.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we went into the cellar, and we found potatoes and we found tubes of cheese.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They had war rations at that time, tubes of cheese, tubes of milk.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We picked up a little lamb that we brought that home.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We talked bicycles.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I mean, it was a free-for-all.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And at one point, George told me to watch the cart with the food while he was going into another house.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And there was some noise going on at the end the street, and I was nosy.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I wanted to see what was going on, and I left the cart for a minute.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And it was gone when I came back.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
